    "title": "Agano Jipya la Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "agano jipya la mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Agano ni ahadi au makubaliano kati ya makundi mawili au watu wawili ambayo kwa kawaida yanajumuisha majukumu kwa kila upande. Mungu alifanya agano na watu wa Israeli kupitia Mose na utoaji wa sheria (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:1-Exod24:18\">Kutoka 19–24</a>). Baadaye, Mungu aliahidi kuanzisha agano jipya na watu wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:31-Jer31:34\">Yeremia 31:31–34</a>). Yesu alianza agano hili jipya (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:19-Luke22:20\">Luka 22:19–20</a>). Anaondoa &quot;pazia&quot; la agano la zamani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14\">2 Wakorintho 3:14</a>). Mtume Paulo anatumia hadithi ya uumbaji kutoka <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1-Gen2:25\">Mwanzo 1–2</a> kueleza kwamba Mungu wa uumbaji pia ni Mungu wa &quot;uumbaji mpya&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4-2Cor4:6\">2 Wakorintho 4:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">5:17</a>). Mungu sasa anajifunua kupitia Yesu Kristo, ambaye analeta Mungu karibu nasi.</p><p>Kwenye Agano Jipya, Mungu, Baba wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo, pia ni Baba yetu kwa sababu ametuchukua kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2 Wakorintho 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal4:7\">Wagalatia 3:26–4:7</a>). Yeye ni Mungu Mwaminifu ambaye ahadi za Agano la Kale zinatimia katika Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:18-2Cor1:22\">2 Wakorintho 1:18–22</a>). Yeye ni mwandishi wa upatanisho. Kristo alikua njia ambayo Mungu alipatana na dunia yenye dhambi na yeye mwenyewe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18-2Cor5:21\">5:18–21</a>). Yesu Kristo alikua mwanadamu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">8:9</a>). Aliachia nguvu za kuokoa za Mungu na uadilifu ili kurejesha uhusiano kati ya Mungu na dunia.</p><p>Chini ya agano jipya, Mungu anatuma Roho wake kuishi miongoni mwa watu wake. Roho huwapa Wakristo uzima, uhuru, na uwezo wa kumtii Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:6\">3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:17-2Cor3:18\">17–18</a>). Roho hutunganisha na Kristo na kuhakikisha wokovu wetu kamili katika ufufuo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:22\">1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1-2Cor5:5\">5:1–5</a>). Huu ni wakati ambapo miili ya kufa ya Wakristo itabadilika kuwa miili ya utukufu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:57\">1 Wakorintho 15:42–57</a>). Paulo anaeleza kwa kina tumaini hili katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1-2Cor5:10\">2 Wakorintho 5:1–10</a>. Hili litakuwa ni matokeo ya mwisho ya agano jipya ambalo Mungu amefanya na watu wake.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1-Gen9:17\">Mwanzo 9:1–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:9\">12:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1-Gen15:21\">15:1–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:3-Exod19:6\">Kutoka 19:3–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5-2Sam7:16\">2 Samweli 7:5–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13-1Chr10:14\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 10:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:20-Isa59:21\">Isaya 59:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17-Isa65:25\">65:17–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:1-Jer3:10\">Yeremia 2:1–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:31-Jer31:34\">31:31–34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:27-Matt26:29\">Mathayo 26:27–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:20\">Luka 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:23-1Cor11:32\">1 Wakorintho 11:23–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:4-2Cor3:18\">2 Wakorintho 3:4–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4-2Cor4:6\">4:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:6-Heb8:13\">Waebrania 8:6–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:11-Heb9:28\">9:11–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1-Heb10:25\">10:1–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:18-Heb12:24\">12:18–24</a></p>",
